        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6962",
        "content": "O noble piece of justice! mine author exclaims: and who is he that would not rather lose his seat and robes, forfeit his office, than give sentence against the majesty of beauty?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
